---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Tools" description="Current recommended resources and guides for Last War: Survival players, plus planned future calculators and tools.">
  <h1>Tools</h1>

  <h2>Our Calculators</h2>
  <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
    <li><a href="/tools/resource-chest-calculator" class="text-[#f59e0b] hover:underline"><strong>Resource Chest Calculator</strong></a> — what your banked chests are worth at your HQ level, and how much waiting adds. See the page for sources and confidence levels on the underlying numbers.</li>
    <li><a href="/tools/speedup-calculator" class="text-[#f59e0b] hover:underline"><strong>Speedup Calculator</strong></a> — total your speedup inventory by category and check whether it covers your next build, research, or training target.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="mt-6">Other Recommended Tools</h2>
  <p class="text-[#8a96b0]">Current recommended tools:</p>
  <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
    <li><strong>Written guides on this site</strong> — currently the best and most up-to-date resource for new/mid-game players</li>
    <li><strong>Reddit (r/LastWarMobileGame)</strong> — search for recent visual squad guides or server-specific advice</li>
    <li><strong>Your alliance</strong> — the fastest way to get tested, server-specific advice</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="mt-6">Coming Soon (Phase 2)</h2>
  <ul class="text-sm">
    <li>Hero EXP calculator</li>
    <li>Hero upgrade cost estimator</li>
    <li>Interactive squad builder</li>
    <li>Event calendar with reminders</li>
  </ul>
</Layout>